file: MessageUpdateEvent.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Event\\Lifecycle\\MessageUpdateEvent"
type: readonly final class
summary: Represents a domain event signaling an update to a message within the lifecycle of an agent interaction. This immutable value object encapsulates the context required to track message state changes without side effects.
